  "comment_text": {
    "sn8.12:1.2": "The chapter culminates with Vaṅgīsa revealing his own spiritual journey. The version at <a href='https://suttacentral.net/thag21/en/sujato#45.1'>Thag 21:45.1</a> is more detailed. ",
    "sn8.12:2.1": "This verse is plural, presumably referring to a troupe of wandering bards. | For “drunk on poetry” see <a href='https://suttacentral.net/sn4.13/en/sujato#2.1'>SN 4.13:2.1</a> and note. "
  },
