  "root_text": {
    "sn8.12:0.1": "Saṁyutta Nikāya 8.12 ",
    "sn8.12:0.2": "1. Vaṅgīsavagga ",
    "sn8.12:0.3": "Vaṅgīsasutta ",
    "sn8.12:1.1": "Ekaṁ samayaṁ āyasmā vaṅgīso sāvatthiyaṁ viharati jetavane anāthapiṇḍikassa ārāme. ",
    "sn8.12:1.2": "Tena kho pana samayena āyasmā vaṅgīso aciraarahattappatto hutvā vimuttisukhaṁ paṭisaṁvedī tāyaṁ velāyaṁ imā gāthāyo abhāsi: ",
    "sn8.12:2.1": "“Kāveyyamattā vicarimha pubbe, ",
    "sn8.12:2.2": "Gāmā gāmaṁ purā puraṁ; ",
    "sn8.12:2.3": "Athaddasāma sambuddhaṁ, ",
    "sn8.12:2.4": "Saddhā no upapajjatha. ",
    "sn8.12:3.1": "So me dhammamadesesi, ",
    "sn8.12:3.2": "khandhāyatanadhātuyo; ",
    "sn8.12:3.3": "Tassāhaṁ dhammaṁ sutvāna, ",
    "sn8.12:3.4": "pabbajiṁ anagāriyaṁ. ",
    "sn8.12:4.1": "Bahunnaṁ vata atthāya, ",
    "sn8.12:4.2": "bodhiṁ ajjhagamā muni; ",
    "sn8.12:4.3": "Bhikkhūnaṁ bhikkhunīnañca, ",
    "sn8.12:4.4": "ye niyāmagataddasā. ",
    "sn8.12:5.1": "Svāgataṁ vata me āsi, ",
    "sn8.12:5.2": "mama buddhassa santike; ",
    "sn8.12:5.3": "Tisso vijjā anuppattā, ",
    "sn8.12:5.4": "kataṁ buddhassa sāsanaṁ. ",
    "sn8.12:6.1": "Pubbenivāsaṁ jānāmi, ",
    "sn8.12:6.2": "Dibbacakkhuṁ visodhitaṁ; ",
    "sn8.12:6.3": "Tevijjo iddhipattomhi, ",
    "sn8.12:6.4": "Cetopariyāyakovido”ti. ",
    "sn8.12:7.0": "Tassuddānaṁ ",
    "sn8.12:7.1": "Nikkhantaṁ arati ceva, ",
    "sn8.12:7.2": "pesalā atimaññanā; ",
    "sn8.12:7.3": "Ānandena subhāsitā, ",
    "sn8.12:7.4": "sāriputtapavāraṇā; ",
    "sn8.12:7.5": "Parosahassaṁ koṇḍañño, ",
    "sn8.12:7.6": "moggallānena gaggarā; ",
    "sn8.12:7.7": "Vaṅgīsena dvādasāti. ",
    "sn8.12:7.8": "Vaṅgīsasaṁyuttaṁ samattaṁ. "
  },
  "translation_text": {
    "sn8.12:0.1": "Linked Discourses 8.12 ",
    "sn8.12:0.2": "1. With Vaṅgīsa ",
    "sn8.12:0.3": "With Vaṅgīsa ",
    "sn8.12:1.1": "At one time Venerable Vaṅgīsa was staying near Sāvatthī in Jeta’s Grove, Anāthapiṇḍika’s monastery. ",
    "sn8.12:1.2": "Now at that time Vaṅgīsa had recently attained perfection. While experiencing the bliss of freedom, on that occasion he recited these verses: ",
    "sn8.12:2.1": "“We used to wander, drunk on poetry, ",
    "sn8.12:2.2": "village to village, town to town. ",
    "sn8.12:2.3": "Then we saw the Buddha, ",
    "sn8.12:2.4": "and faith arose in us. ",
    "sn8.12:3.1": "He taught me Dhamma: ",
    "sn8.12:3.2": "the aggregates, sense fields, and elements. ",
    "sn8.12:3.3": "When I heard his teaching ",
    "sn8.12:3.4": "I went forth to homelessness. ",
    "sn8.12:4.1": "It was truly for the benefit of many ",
    "sn8.12:4.2": "that the sage achieved awakening—",
    "sn8.12:4.3": "for the monks and for the nuns ",
    "sn8.12:4.4": "who see that they’ve reached certainty. ",
    "sn8.12:5.1": "It was so welcome for me ",
    "sn8.12:5.2": "to be in the presence of the Buddha. ",
    "sn8.12:5.3": "I’ve attained the three knowledges, ",
    "sn8.12:5.4": "and fulfilled the Buddha’s instructions. ",
    "sn8.12:6.1": "I know my past lives, ",
    "sn8.12:6.2": "my clairvoyance is purified, ",
    "sn8.12:6.3": "I am master of three knowledges, <j>attained in psychic power, ",
    "sn8.12:6.4": "expert in encompassing the minds of others.” ",
    "sn8.12:7.1": "",
    "sn8.12:7.2": "",
    "sn8.12:7.3": "",
    "sn8.12:7.4": "",
    "sn8.12:7.5": "",
    "sn8.12:7.6": "",
    "sn8.12:7.7": "",
    "sn8.12:7.8": "The Linked Discourses with Vaṅgīsa are complete. "
  },
